data.description: Welcome to this charming two story in the heart of Saint Paul! Located just one block from Beaver Lake, this 3 bedroom property offers a wonderful balance of formal and informal spaces. The main level greets you with beautiful hardwood floors and a large living space with fireplace, as well as a primary bedroom that offers the flexibility of also being used for formal dining. Upstairs you'll find two additional bedrooms large enough for office areas in both rooms! The finished lower-level is perfect for entertaining and relaxing, and offers additional full bath. This home strikes a perfect balance cozy and classic, allowing you to create the ideal atmosphere for any occasion. New roof October 2023. Don't miss it!
